{"tid":1240442,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[集氣]希望有議員同律師幫手跟進，現時警察問題","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T15:03:10.000Z","uid":14921,"like":233,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"e988b446ce38256547b1ae6578bfd20d31bf56d3","tid":1240442,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:43:21.000Z","msg":"眼見而家警方權力問題過大<br />\n監警會又只係無牙老虎<br />\n希望有議員同律師可以幫手跟進以下幾點問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一。制服沒有展示警員編號</span></span><br />\n最大問題係速龍小隊沒有展示警員身份，使未能確認其警員身份進行投訴或指控<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXvQBfS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXvQBfS.png&h=f4fc88d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任何部隊</span></strong>的警員編號必須清楚展示於<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正面</span></strong>及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">背面</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qCcjuBH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqCcjuBH.jpg&h=d552d7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二。便衣警員拒絕出示委任證</span></span><br />\n有便衣警員行使警權時拒絕出示委任證<br />\n違反了<span style=\"color: red;\">(PGO 20-16)</span><br />\n（一）便衣人員與巿民接觸時，不論是否當值，在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KbwTy6w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKbwTy6w.png&h=215a5691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議：警員拒絕出示委任證刑事化，一來有冒警之嫌，二來就算真係警察，合理懷疑其警員為了進行不合法事情／濫用警權而拒絕出示委任證<br />\n將此類案件提出刑事起訴，而非只是降職或停職審查。<br />\n而市民有權發現警員拒出示委任證後，市民有權以公民拘捕權拘捕警察<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港法例221章101A <br />\n&quot;任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，可使用就當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。&quot; </span><br />\n否則，該警員離開後事件只會不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三。警方濫用武力鎮壓</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqM8n30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqM8n30.jpg&h=8c2f161c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗都唔洗我多講<br />\n警方濫用催淚彈，布袋彈等<br />\n催淚彈水平射出／布袋彈向頭部射出<br />\n都係違反現時警方指引<br />\n建議：違反指引刑事化，違反指引（例如射向頭部）可隨時致命，而警察有使用槍械權，必須更加嚴格管制！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四。警方有義務提交警員名單</span></span><br />\n有鑑於警員編號展示，出示委任證等問題<br />\n市民投訴無門<br />\n建議立法會有權要求警方提交名單<br />\n包括：指示開槍及開槍之警察，拒絕出示委任證之警察以及其他濫用暴力之警察<br />\n而唔係無法指出邊位警察就無法向警監會投訴，以便投訴或指控既進行跟進<br />\n<br />\n法律知識有限<br />\n集氣推到有議員同律師跟進<br />\n諗到再講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人。加油</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9b605b5786299ec88388682efb3b3da320581c8c","tid":1240442,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87f3d85d680514aebaf1269acb2da83e013b1c12","tid":1240442,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d73747cee241ecc8dfdba6afe2e7df894feb8c","tid":1240442,"uid":14921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"係咪大家睇完覺得無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c5da020744d59f56ff9bf955da24410571628f","tid":1240442,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00cc8e296537198d2bad10dae7d8310cc0c33063","tid":1240442,"uid":140354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4d73747cee241ecc8dfdba6afe2e7df894feb8c","tid":1240442,"uid":14921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"係咪大家睇完覺得無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:09:23.000Z","msg":"同意要追究到底<img sr